column2: "Hey, I saw it! Saw what? That black figure people keep talking about!"
"You haven't heard? There's been reports of several people spotting an all-black figure on Naberius."
"I don't know how to describe it, except he really was wearing all black."
"Details? Like I have enough courage to do that! He was creepy enough from a distance!"
"I'm fine with having seen him and come out alive."
